			"questionAnalysis": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;word-break:break-word;\"><span>本题主要考查了数与形中的找规律问题，根据</span><span>1</span><span>张方桌能坐：</span>$2+2=4$<span>，</span><span>2</span><span>张方桌能坐：</span>$2\\times 2+2=6$<span>人，</span><span>3</span><span>张方桌能坐：</span>$2\\times 3+2=8$<span>人，即可得出</span><span>10</span><span>张方桌能坐</span>$2\\times 10+2=22$<span>，用</span>$\\left(32-2\\right)\\div 2=15$<span>，即可得出要坐</span><span>32</span><span>人需要</span>$\\left(32-2\\right)\\div 2=15$<span>张桌子，总结规律即</span><span>n</span><span>张方桌拼在一起能坐</span>$2n+2$<span>人．</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span>解：</span><span>1</span><span>张方桌能坐：</span>$2+2=4$<span>（人），</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span>2</span><span>张方桌能坐：</span>$2\\times 2+2=6$<span>（人），</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span>3</span><span>张方桌能坐：</span>$2\\times 3+2=8$<span>（人），</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">$\\cdot \\cdot \\cdot$</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span>10</span><span>张方桌能坐：</span>$2\\times 10+2=22$<span>（人），</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span>要坐</span><span>32</span><span>人，需要：</span>$\\left(32-2\\right)\\div 2=15$<span>（张），</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span>n</span><span>张方桌拼在一起能坐</span>$2n+2$<span>人，</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span>故答案为：</span><span>22</span><span>，</span><span>15</span><span>，</span>$2n+2$<span>．</span></p>",
