			"isProcessing": null,
			"questionStem": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\">$4a+8$<span>错写成</span>$4\\times (a+8)$<span>，结果比原来</span><span>（&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）．</span></p>",
			"questionAnalysis": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;word-break:break-word;\"><span>本题考查了用乘法分配律计算含字母的算式，根据乘法分配律，将算式</span>$4\\times (a+8)$<span>去括号得出</span>$4a+4\\times 8$<span>，计算出结果，再求与</span>$4a+8$<span>的差即可，要熟记运算律并能灵活使用</span><span>．</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;word-break:break-word;\"><span>解：</span>$4\\times (a+8)-(4a+8)$</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;word-break:break-word;\">$=4a+32-4a-8$</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;word-break:break-word;\">$=32-8$</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;word-break:break-word;\">$=24$</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;word-break:break-word;\"><span>答：结果比原来多</span><span>24</span><span>．</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;word-break:break-word;\"><span>故选：</span><span>C</span><span>．</span></p>",
