			"questionContent": "解方程或比例．  $\\dfrac{3}{5} = \\dfrac{4.2}{x}$ 解：$\\because \\dfrac{3}{5} = \\dfrac{4.2}{x}$， $\\therefore 3x = 4.2 \\times 5$， (不对) $\\therefore 3x = 21$， $\\therefore x = 7$． $1 - \\dfrac{3}{5}x = \\dfrac{3}{10}$ 解：$1 - \\dfrac{3}{5}x = \\dfrac{3}{10}$， 两边同时乘以 $10$得： $10 - 6x = 3$， 移项得： $-6x = 3 - 10$， 合并同类项得： $-6x = -7$， 系数化为 $1$得： $x = \\dfrac{7}{6}$． $\\dfrac{1}{6} : x = \\dfrac{1}{10} : \\dfrac{1}{4}$ 解：根据比例的基本性质，两外项之积等于两内项之积， $\\because \\dfrac{1}{6} : x = \\dfrac{1}{10} : \\dfrac{1}{4}$， $\\therefore \\dfrac{1}{10}x = \\dfrac{1}{6} \\times \\dfrac{1}{4}$， $\\dots \\dfrac{1}{10}x = \\dfrac{1}{24}$， $\\therefore x = \\dfrac{1}{24} \\times 10$， $\\dots x = \\dfrac{5}{12}$．",
