					"questionContent": "$\\dfrac{1}{6} : x = \\dfrac{1}{10} : \\dfrac{1}{4}$ 解：根据比例的基本性质，两外项之积等于两内项之积， $\\because \\dfrac{1}{6} : x = \\dfrac{1}{10} : \\dfrac{1}{4}$， $\\therefore \\dfrac{1}{10}x = \\dfrac{1}{6} \\times \\dfrac{1}{4}$， $\\dots \\dfrac{1}{10}x = \\dfrac{1}{24}$， $\\therefore x = \\dfrac{1}{24} \\times 10$， $\\dots x = \\dfrac{5}{12}$．",
