					"questionAnalysis": "<p style=\"text-indent: 0pt; \">解：根据比例的基本性质，两外项之积等于两内项之积，</p>\n    <p style=\"text-indent: 0pt; \">$\\because \\dfrac{1}{6} : x = \\dfrac{1}{10} : \\dfrac{1}{4}$，</p>\n    <p style=\"text-indent: 0pt; \">$\\therefore \\dfrac{1}{10}x = \\dfrac{1}{6} \\times \\dfrac{1}{4}$，</p>\n    <p style=\"text-indent: 0pt; \">$\\dots \\dfrac{1}{10}x = \\dfrac{1}{24}$，</p>\n    <p style=\"text-indent: 0pt; \">$\\therefore x = \\dfrac{1}{24} \\times 10$，</p>\n    <p style=\"text-indent: 0pt; \">$\\dots x = \\dfrac{5}{12}$．</p>",
