			"questionContent": "求下图阴影部分的面积． 解： 连接 $OE$ ． $\\because$ 四边形 $ABCD$ 是正方形，边长为 $8$， $\\therefore \\angle DAB = 90^{\\circ}$，$AB = BC = 8$， $\\because AC$ 是正方形 $ABCD$ 的对角线， $\\therefore \\angle BAC = 45^{\\circ}$， $\\because O$ 是 $AB$ 的中点，以 $AB$ 为直径在正方形内作半圆， $\\therefore OA = OB = OE = 4$， $\\therefore \\angle OAE = \\angle OEA = 45^{\\circ}$， $\\therefore \\angle AOE = 180^{\\circ} - \\angle OAE - \\angle OEA = 90^{\\circ}$， $\\therefore \\angle BOE = 180^{\\circ} - \\angle AOE = 90^{\\circ}$， $\\therefore S_{\\triangle ABC} = \\dfrac{1}{2} \\times AB \\times BC = \\dfrac{1}{2} \\times 8 \\times 8 = 32$， $\\therefore S_{\\triangle AOE} = \\dfrac{1}{2} \\times OA \\times OE = \\dfrac{1}{2} \\times 4 \\times 4 = 8$， $\\because \\angle BOE = 90^{\\circ}$， $\\therefore S_{\\text{扇形 } BOE} = \\dfrac{90}{360} \\times \\pi \\times OE^2 = \\dfrac{1}{4} \\times \\pi \\times 4^2 = 4\\pi$， $\\because S_{\\triangle ABC} = S_{\\triangle AOE} + S_{\\text{扇形 } BOE} + S_{\\text{阴影}}$， $\\therefore S_{\\text{阴影}} = S_{\\triangle ABC} - S_{\\triangle AOE} - S_{\\text{扇形 } BOE}$ $\\therefore S_{\\text{阴影}} = 32 - 8 - 4\\pi = 24 - 4\\pi$． 故答案为：$24 - 4\\pi$．",
			"questionInfo": {
				"answer": "<p style=\"text-indent: 0pt; \">$24 - 4\\pi$</p>",
				"options": [],
				"analysis": "<p style=\"text-indent: 0pt; \">解：</p>\n    <img src=\"https://tiku-1252350207.cos.ap-beijing.myqcloud.com/k12-paper/73-1780751955084.png\" alt=\"#cetz.canvas({\n\n  import cetz.draw: *\n\n  rect((0,0), (4,4), stroke: 0.5pt + gray)\n\n  fill(rgb(&quot;d0d0d0&quot;))\n\n  stroke(none)\n\n  merge-path({\n\n    line((2,2), (4,4))\n\n    line((4,4), (4,0))\n\n    arc((4,0), start: 0deg, stop: 90deg, radius: 2)\n\n  })\n\n  stroke(0.8pt + black)\n\n  rect((0,0), (4,4))\n\n  line((0,0), (4,4))\n\n  arc((4,0), start: 0deg, stop: 180deg, radius: 2)\n\n  stroke((paint: gray, dash: &quot;dashed&quot;))\n\n  line((2,0), (2,2))\n\n  content((0,0), [ #latex(`A`) ], anchor: &quot;north-east&quot;)\n\n  content((4,0), [ #latex(`B`) ], anchor: &quot;north-west&quot;)\n\n  content((4,4), [ #latex(`C`) ], anchor: &quot;south-west&quot;)\n\n  content((0,4), [ #latex(`D`) ], anchor: &quot;south-east&quot;)\n\n  content((2,0), [ #latex(`O`) ], anchor: &quot;north&quot;)\n\n  content((2,2), [ #latex(`E`) ], anchor: &quot;south-east&quot;)\n\n})\">\n    <p style=\"text-indent: 0pt; \">连接 $OE$ ．</p>\n    <p style=\"text-indent: 0pt; \">$\\because$ 四边形 $ABCD$ 是正方形，边长为 $8$，</p>\n    <p style=\"text-indent: 0pt; \">$\\therefore \\angle DAB = 90^{\\circ}$，$AB = BC = 8$，</p>\n    <p style=\"text-indent: 0pt; \">$\\because AC$ 是正方形 $ABCD$ 的对角线，</p>\n    <p style=\"text-indent: 0pt; \">$\\therefore \\angle BAC = 45^{\\circ}$，</p>\n    <p style=\"text-indent: 0pt; \">$\\because O$ 是 $AB$ 的中点，以 $AB$ 为直径在正方形内作半圆，</p>\n    <p style=\"text-indent: 0pt; \">$\\therefore OA = OB = OE = 4$，</p>\n    <p style=\"text-indent: 0pt; \">$\\therefore \\angle OAE = \\angle OEA = 45^{\\circ}$，</p>\n    <p style=\"text-indent: 0pt; \">$\\therefore \\angle AOE = 180^{\\circ} - \\angle OAE - \\angle OEA = 90^{\\circ}$，</p>\n    <p style=\"text-indent: 0pt; \">$\\therefore \\angle BOE = 180^{\\circ} - \\angle AOE = 90^{\\circ}$，</p>\n    <p style=\"text-indent: 0pt; \">$\\therefore S_{\\triangle ABC} = \\dfrac{1}{2} \\times AB \\times BC = \\dfrac{1}{2} \\times 8 \\times 8 = 32$，</p>\n    <p style=\"text-indent: 0pt; \">$\\therefore S_{\\triangle AOE} = \\dfrac{1}{2} \\times OA \\times OE = \\dfrac{1}{2} \\times 4 \\times 4 = 8$，</p>\n    <p style=\"text-indent: 0pt; \">$\\because \\angle BOE = 90^{\\circ}$，</p>\n    <p style=\"text-indent: 0pt; \">$\\therefore S_{\\text{扇形 } BOE} = \\dfrac{90}{360} \\times \\pi \\times OE^2 = \\dfrac{1}{4} \\times \\pi \\times 4^2 = 4\\pi$，</p>\n    <p style=\"text-indent: 0pt; \">$\\because S_{\\triangle ABC} = S_{\\triangle AOE} + S_{\\text{扇形 } BOE} + S_{\\text{阴影}}$，</p>\n    <p style=\"text-indent: 0pt; \">$\\therefore S_{\\text{阴影}} = S_{\\triangle ABC} - S_{\\triangle AOE} - S_{\\text{扇形 } BOE}$</p>\n    <p style=\"text-indent: 0pt; \">$\\therefore S_{\\text{阴影}} = 32 - 8 - 4\\pi = 24 - 4\\pi$．</p>\n    <p style=\"text-indent: 0pt; \">故答案为：$24 - 4\\pi$．</p>",
				"stem": "<p style=\"text-indent: 0pt; \">求下图阴影部分的面积．</p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: right\"><img src=\"https://img.xkw.com/dksih/QBM/2019/6/1/2216198352404480/2217167164653569/STEM/def71d3f-c1b7-493e-8afe-8ebcb81cafd8.png\"></p>"
