					"questionStem": "<p style=\"text-indent: 0pt; \">每位小客人喝了多少毫升？</p>",
					"questionAnalysis": "<p style=\"text-indent: 0pt; \">解：根据题意和图示可知，圆柱形杯子的底面直径为 $6\\text{ cm}$，高为 $10\\text{ cm}$，</p>\n    <p style=\"text-indent: 0pt; \">$\\because$ 圆柱形杯子的底面半径为：</p>\n    <p style=\"text-indent: 0pt; \">$r = 6 \\div 2 = 3\\text{ cm}$，</p>\n    <p style=\"text-indent: 0pt; \">$\\therefore$ 圆柱形杯子的容积为：</p>\n    <p style=\"text-indent: 0pt; \">$V = 3.14 \\times 3^2 \\times 10 = 282.6\\text{ cm}^3$，</p>\n    <p style=\"text-indent: 0pt; \">$\\because 1\\text{ cm}^3 = 1\\text{ mL}$，</p>\n    <p style=\"text-indent: 0pt; \">$\\therefore 282.6\\text{ cm}^3 = 282.6\\text{ mL}$，</p>\n    <p style=\"text-indent: 0pt; \">$\\therefore$ 每位小客人喝了 $282.6$ 毫升．</p>",
